# Large ephemeris binary — fetched at build time by scripts/fetch-ephemeris.mjs
# (or manually: curl -o public/de421.bsp https://ssd.jpl.nasa.gov/ftp/eph/planets/bsp/de421.bsp)
public/de421.bsp
# Full Hipparcos catalogue — NOT needed at runtime (the single Spica record is embedded
# in src/lib/pyodide/index.js). Only appears if someone re-downloads it.
hip_main.dat*

